    Woodbridge High School

    KANJ Cine Star Nite 2025- Magic of Cinema, Music, and Comedy!!!

    Kerala Association of New Jersey (KANJ) is excited to bring you an amazing evening as Cine Star Nite 2025 brings the magic of cinema, music, and comedy to life! Have you booked your tickets yet? Seats are limited!! Reserve them now

    Time & Location

    May 18, 2025, 5:00 PM 8:30 PM

    Woodbridge High School, 1 Samuel Lupo Pl, Woodbridge, NJ 07095, USA

    About the event

    Kerala Association of New Jersey (KANJ) is excited to bring you an amazing evening as Cine Star Nite 2025 brings the magic of cinema, music, and comedy to life! Featuring a dazzling lineup of your favorite movie stars, celebrated musicians, and hilarious comedians- Shwetha Menon, Malavika Menon, Sreenath Shivashankaran, Rahul Madhav, Manikkuttan, Manoj George, Mahesh Kunjumon, Reshma Raghavendra, Anoop Kovalam, Palakkadu Murali this star-studded event promises to be the entertainment highlight of the year.


    From breathtaking performances by chart-topping artists to laugh-out-loud moments with the funniest comics, KANJ Cine Star Nite 2025 is a celebration of creativity and glamour.


    Have you booked your tickets yet? Seats are limited!! Reserve them now while early bird specials last.
